{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563880/extras/ks1b234bbbs222233222222222b.gif?t=1735003906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Soar through the skies on the back of a winged beast. Explore the depths of a painstakingly rendered world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563880/extras/ks1b234bbbs222233222222222bb.gif?t=1735003906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">encountering new gear to customize your play style and craft Iria's look to your vision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563880/extras/ks1b234bbbs222233222222222bbb.gif?t=1735003906\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ghost Hand is a Soviet inspired fantasy Metroidvania. Immerse yourself in a vast, atmospheric fantasy world, brimming with secrets to uncover and a story that would make any JRPG proud.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a art style that blends seamlessly the oil pain pixel art aesthetics of Owlboy in a 2.5D environment similar to Klonoa, in a world with Exploration and Character customization inspired by the likes of Symphony of the Night with Ori inspired Bosses, while having the capability of mounting a Dragon and toasting your enemies like you would Drakengard.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563880/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735003906","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563880/page.bg.jpg?t=1735003906","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2563880/ab280c9db5f643707c6796d51f7047bd199edf76/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735003906","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.ak